ActOther Than Statutory Authority
PrecisAppointment of SÉBASTIEN BEAULIEU as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Guinea Bissau with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Cabo Verde, and as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of The Gambia, with residence in Dakar; MARK GLAUSER as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of the Marshall Islands, with residence in Canberra; MARCY GROSSMAN as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the United Arab Emirates; ALISON LECLAIRE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Russian Federation; DOUGLAS SCOTT PROUDFOOT as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of South Sudan; and NELL STEWART as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Kingdom of Morocco.
